      <title>新泽西州交通局首席执行官 Corbett 将在任职七年后辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nj-transit-ceo-to-resign-after-seven-years-running-the-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新泽西州交通局首席执行官兼总裁凯文·科贝特 (Kevin Corbett) 将于下个月卸任，他已执掌全美最大的公共交通提供商之一近七年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nj-transit-ceo-to-resign-after-seven-years-running-the-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
