      <title>加纳前总统获得巨大授权解决通货膨胀问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/ghana-election-mahama-faces-slew-of-challenges-after-biggest-mandate-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳选举前总统约翰·马哈马重返他八年前的职位，赋予他强有力的授权来解决这个西非国家沉重的债务负担和高昂的生活成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/ghana-election-mahama-faces-slew-of-challenges-after-biggest-mandate-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杠杆中国 ETF 看涨押注净赚 1.38 亿美元账面收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/huge-levered-china-etf-bullish-bets-net-138-million-paper-gain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去一周，交易员在跟踪中国指数的小型杠杆交易所交易基金中买入了价值数百万股的看涨期权，由于北京高层领导人表示明年将提供更有力的经济支持，股价飙升，账面收益超过 1.3 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/huge-levered-china-etf-bullish-bets-net-138-million-paper-gain</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:18:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街强劲反弹在 CPI 上涨中受挫：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市在上涨之后回落，市场有望创下 2019 年以来的最佳年度表现，交易员正在等待有助于影响美联储利率前景的关键通胀数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 22:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
